snippet.textDisplay: It’s a shame that people have negative experiences at luxury hand bag brands. It always concerns me to hear of situations where service is so poor considering luxury handbag sales have been consistently trending down over the last several years. I find myself trying to be much more thoughtful about those type of purchases. It’s a conflict, I love the history the luxury brands and  want them to continue to thrive but as awareness about leather sourcing /workers conditions becomes more public it causes me pause.
